<HEADLINE> Ethiopia Lays off 15,460 Civil Servants in Reform </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, March 4 (Xinhua) -- Ethiopia today said that its
economic reform program has laid off 15,460 civil servants.
</P>
