Berri arrived here Sunday heading a parliamentary delegation
on a three-day visit.
</P>
<P>
During his stay here, he met with Kuwaiti Amir Sheikh Jaber
al-Ahmad al-Sabah, Crown Prince and Prime Minister Sheikh Saad
al-Abdullah al-Salem al-Sabah, Speaker Ahmed Abdul Aziz al
Sadoun and other senior Kuwaiti officials.
</P>
<P>
He said upon his arrival in Kuwait that he was here to express
his gratitude for the assistance extended by Kuwait to his country.
</P>
<P>
