the 16-nation Alliance.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the Royal Institute of International Affairs today,
Solana said: "I do not want to minimize the difficulties but I
believe they (the Russians) are interested in partnership with
NATO and we will conclude one."
</P>
<P>
