<P>
BEIJING, March 5 (Xinhua) -- Local committees of the Chinese
People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) have mainly
worked to promote economic advances by providing needy suggestions
based on investigations for local governments, according to
speakers at a press conference organized by the CPPCC National
Committee in session here.
</P>
<P>
In Guangdong, local committees of the CPPCC have performed
their function as advisory bodies to serve the province's opening
to the outside world, said Guo Rongchang, chairman of the CPPCC
Guangdong Committee.
</P>
<P>
Late last year, he said, a special meeting was held by the
committee on development of foreign-funded enterprises.
</P>
