attract investment from small and medium-sized enterprises,
enhance cooperation with consortia and improve the management of
existing overseas-funded enterprises.
</P>
<P>
Sun Han, chairman of the CPPCC Jiangsu Committee, talked of
CPPCC's role in promoting scientific and democratic
decision-making by the Jiangsu provincial government. He said the
CPPCC Jiangsu Committee has conducted 31 investigations for the
provincial government to help formulate the provincial Ninth
Five-Year Plan and Long-Range Objectives Through the Year 2010.
</P>
<P>
The suggestions put forward by the CPPCC members, he said, have
been forwarded to related departments and localities. Some
of them have been adopted in decision-making and policies, he
said. 
