Authority (BCAA) has banned aircraft owned by the Nigeria Airways
from flying to London, the Daily Times reported today.
</P>
<P>
The report said the ban came in the wake of alleged
irregularities in the insurance papers of the national carriers
of Nigeria.
</P>
<P>
It said the BCAA has earlier asked the Nigeria Airways to seek
clarifications on the insurance cover for its fleet.
</P>
<P>
