He said that the management of the airline is already working with
the National Insurance Corporation of Nigeria (NICON) to resolve the
issue.
</P>
<P>
The report said NICON has last month withdrawn its insurance
cover from the airline over default in premium payment.
</P>
<P>
Managing Director of the airline Peter Gana said at a press
conference two weeks ago that Nigeria Airways has been meeting
its insurance obligations. 
