Training Institute in Arusha, Daily News reported today.
</P>
<P>
The reports said the course is part of Overseas Development
Administration (ODA) (of Great Britain) post-Beijing project
aimed at developing the grass-roots women by training them in
different sectors, in an effort to raise their standard of
living.
</P>
<P>
