course will be held at the Uyole Agricultural Training Center in
Mbeya for Mbeya and Iringa Regions.
</P>
<P>
During the course, the participants learn how to make yoghurt,
cheese, butter and ghee. Processing milk is considered to be a
last solution to destruction of the product due to lack of
equipment to preserve it in the rural areas.
</P>
<P>
The first post ODA/Beijing course attended by 40 women
handicraft workers last December in Dar es salaam has already
produced the desired fruits as the quality of products produced
by the women have improved tremendously. 
