September until returning in February. He suffered a sprained
left ankle in a first-round loss in Memphis in February.
</P>
<P>
Sanchez took the first set, reeling off the last four games,
including a pair of service breaks.
</P>
<P>
He went up 4-2 in the second with a crucial break in the sixth
game and held on to warp up the victory. 
